profile:
Do you need to store furniture or equipment? Mini Entrepôt Longueuil offers more than 900 units of high quality storage on the South Shore of Montreal. We supply 80 different unit configurations, heated or non-heated, for residential, commercial or industrial use.
We guarantee high security thanks to surveillance cameras display on every building. Moreover, the magnetic card system allows an individual access to your locals. We also offer a wide range of complementary services like forklift reservation, individual mail box, layered storage and padlocks selling on the spot.
Chose Mini Entrepôt Longueuil of Montreal! Visit the minientrepotlongueuil.com
